name: GoCast
tag_list: live-video, shared-video, video-communications, group-video, mobile-video, live-sharing
overview:
GoCast enables live shared video on any device, including smart phones, tablets, and computers.

GoCast offers free live interactive chat for the most popular devices: IOS, Android, Macintosh, PC, and Linux. Users in a GoCast session can communicate to the group or to private individuals via text messaging. Users may also share Internet content to anyone logged into the session.

GoCast is based on a cloud-based infrastructure. GoCast’s engine enhances video and audio quality, while minimizing network operating expenditures.
